

=Bio=

My name is Dan Benjamin and I co-founded RepStamp in 2012. RepStamp is creating a universal reputation system for e-commerce marketplaces. Meaning, we allow sellers to aggregate their online identities into our system, we then calculate their reputation score and finally let them carry that score with them, creating a virtual portable identity in the e-commerce world.


